<section class="focus-block">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Putting the Focus on the Brand.</h2>
    <p>
      Our approach delivers real results — putting your business in front of the
      right audience. You build the product. We make sure the world notices.
    </p>
    <p class="tag">Your brand deserves nothing less.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .focus-block { padding: 4rem 0 2.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .focus-block h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--bp-ink);
  }
  .focus-block p {
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--bp-muted);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }
  .focus-block .tag {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--bp-deep);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
